{"hash":"839fc319bfd47004a1da58abb890561978b76f3c","data":{"post":{"title":"Dag 2 - Aachen","author":"","date":"2016-12-13","content":"<p>Rise and shine! Ons uitzicht bij het wakker worden.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00838-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00838\"></p>\n<p>Genieten van het ontbijt</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161211_100407-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161211_100407\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161211_100436-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161211_100436\"></p>\n<p>Ordensburg Vogelsang</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00856-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00856\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00863-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00863\"></p>\n<p>Op naar Aachen en daar de kerstmarkt bezoeken.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00895-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00895\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00897-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00897\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00919-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00919\"></p>\n<p>Coole kaarsen.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161211_164605-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161211_164605\"></p>\n<p>Printen!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161211_164105-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161211_164105\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161211_143601-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161211_143601\"></p>\n<p>Waarom ze hier gek zijn op eendjes, weet ik ook niet..</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161211_141432-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161211_141432\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161211_140741-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161211_140741\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161211_140340-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161211_140340\"></p>\n<p>Voor de lunch lekkere hamburgers.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00902-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00902\"></p>\n<p>Waar we hiermee ons weekend afsluiten. Nu terug naar Nederland rijden. Doei!</p>\n","id":"9d0d3df4a82ca8ab558df2c202984f60","path":"/blog/duitsland-2016/dag-2-aachen/","image":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20161211_140340.jpg","category":{"title":"Monschau, Aachen - Duitsland","id":"Monschau, Aachen - Duitsland","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"Dag 1 - Monschau","path":"/blog/duitsland-2016/dag-1-monschau/","id":"e00c3cc58b59d5a440baf9b8327f30e6","excerpt":"Dit keer lekker met de auto op pad. Direct aangekomen bij onze bestemming in Monschau..."}},{"node":{"title":"Dag 2 - Aachen","path":"/blog/duitsland-2016/dag-2-aachen/","id":"9d0d3df4a82ca8ab558df2c202984f60","excerpt":"Rise and shine! Ons uitzicht bij het wakker worden..."}}]}}}},"context":{}}